Introduction

Shin Yeon Suh is a South Korean singer and actress under MUE A Entertainment. She is a former member of the girl group gugudan under the stage name Hana.

On the 24th August 2021, a source from FN Entertainment confirmed that Hana had joined their company. She would from then on continue with her acting career, going by her birthname, Shin Bo Ra. Sometime in 2022, it was revealed that Hana had left FN Entertainment after her contract had expired after exactly a year and decided not to renew.

On February 21, 2023, it was revealed that Hana had signed with newly-established agency MUE A Entertainment. She would continue her activities as an actress through the stage name Shin Yeon Suh.
